    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six powerplant with high-pressure VANOS and individual throttle bodies. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a reinforced rear subframe and updated rod bearings. The suspension utilizes a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, providing exceptional lateral grip and communicative feedback. While the exterior shows minor road patina consistent with spirited use, the chassis remains rigid and the powertrain delivers crisp, linear throttle response through the entire 8,000 RPM range. A driver-focused machine with sorted internals, ready for the canyons.",
      "price": 34500.0,
