      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity to own a well-cared-for example that balances performance with daily usability. The exterior retains a high-gloss finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper consistent with careful road use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather upholstery remains supple with only light natural creasing on the driver's seat bolster, and all original trim pieces are intact. Every electronic feature, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, operates flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is robust; it has a complete service history, with a recent oil change and brake inspection performed just last month. The engine idles smoothly and provides confident acceleration, while the steering remains precise and free of vibrations. It is a turn-key vehicle that has been treated with respect and is ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 34500.0,
